26/09/11,"- In reference to their... In reference to their earlier letter dated 24.09.11 (news disseminated by DSE on 25.09.11), the Bank has further informed that record date for EGM has been mentioned as 02.10.11 instead of 04.10.11 inadvertently. The correct record date is 04.10.11. Other information of the EGM as announced earlier"
25/09/11,"- The Bank has informed... The Bank has informed that the Board of Directors of the Bank has decided to change face value of the Bank from Tk. 100.00 each to Tk. 10.00 each subject to approval of Bangladesh Bank, SEC and shareholders in the EGM. Date of EGM: 28.10.11, Time of EGM: 10:00 AM, Venue of EGM: Institution of Diploma Engineers' Bangladesh. Record Date for EGM: 02.10.11"
